  "detailed_description": "<h1>关于我们</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >了解小小群雄最新进展，请关注：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：895059729</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站：高达猴</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Little Heroes is an ancient war-themed game. Players will play the role of a lord at the beginning and conquer the surrounding areas. Players can recruit new soldiers through the recruitment hall and train them in the barracks. Develop agriculture and market to increase the income of the area under your jurisdiction. Go out to conquer the city and seize the territory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>fire attack</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704100/extras/3af00d822cbaba8e8319b77d7948eb1f.poster.avif?t=1764315563\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704100/extras/3af00d822cbaba8e8319b77d7948eb1f.webm?t=1764315563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704100/extras/3af00d822cbaba8e8319b77d7948eb1f.mp4?t=1764315563\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>attack a city</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704100/extras/ea57646d5b8bc6fb94a8c40c4979247c.poster.avif?t=1764315563\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704100/extras/ea57646d5b8bc6fb94a8c40c4979247c.webm?t=1764315563\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2704100/extras/ea57646d5b8bc6